item.title: Entering Your ALL ABOUT ME Era: Turning Your Dreams Into a Reality
item.description:
Welcome to your ‘ME’ Era. Entering your selfish years, and finally allowing yourself to spend time on yourself, and put yourself first. It’s never easy to block yourself off and decide you need to start working on yourself; however listening to this episode was your first step.

In todays episode we talk about envisioning your highest self, and showing up as her, taking baby steps to big habits, creating goals and how to achieve them, manifesting, vision boards, and journaling... Feed: https://audioboom.com/channels/5090538.rss
